{"tid":1182754,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[DC漫畫] 岩岩開始睇重生 想問完左未?","createTime":"2019-06-02T11:56:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T02:04:17.000Z","uid":24626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2270dbc7bd780a8189bad0d235386725353256dc","tid":1182754,"uid":24626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T11:56:46.000Z","msg":"以前果D太多太亂 唔知點入手睇<br />\n所以由重生開始睇 亦都大約知道閃點講乜<br />\n跟住呢個網個次序睇岩唔岩?<br />\n<a href=\"https://manhua.dmzj.com/dcyuzhouchongsheng/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmanhua.dmzj.com%2Fdcyuzhouchongsheng%2F&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=a89cfff8\" target=\"_blank\">https://manhua.dmzj.com/dcyuzhouchongsheng/</a><br />\n不過上年開始就冇更新 之後果D可以去邊到睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4ccb4215ed33c9463660f0014fa2809841a0df","tid":1182754,"uid":213803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:05:07.000Z","msg":"美漫太on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗過追唔知點入手 最後放棄咗"},{"pid":"4cdb655b28efee4c555b2afb0eb29fdf1ec434dc","tid":1182754,"uid":24626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a4ccb4215ed33c9463660f0014fa2809841a0df","tid":1182754,"uid":213803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:05:07.000Z","msg":"美漫太on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗過追唔知點入手 最後放棄咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:04:17.000Z","msg":"睇睇下其實幾有趣..佢同時間有好多故仔講緊<br />\n好多平行空間/時間, 但係間唔中又會相交係某一點<br />\n一唔留心或者唔跟次序就會睇到R晒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw最鍾意睇超凡雙子 兩個細路好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}